Package: INDEED
Title: INtegrated Differential ExprEssion and Differential network analysis for biomarker candidate 
    selection (INDEED)
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Yiming Zuo <yimingzuo@gmail.com> with contributions from Kian Ghaffari and Zhenzhi Li
Maintainer: Yiming Zuo <yimingzuo@gmail.com>
Description: An R package for integrated differential expression and differential network analysis 
    based on omic data for biomarker candidate selection. The differential network is built based on 
    correlation or partial correlation.
License: Artistic-2.0
URL: http://github.com/ressomlab/INDEED
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
